description.plain: Kevin Perez, better known by his stage name Kay Flock, is an upcoming drill artist from The Bronx, New York. He started gaining popularity in late 2020 with the songs “Opp Spotter” and “Shot Down” with frequent collaborator B Lovee. He is also associated with Dougie B, making the trio responsible for “Brotherly Love”, one of their biggest songs to date.
